page.title: 06NORTH WALSHAM
page.content: North Walsham is a fairly big market town with a population of about 8,600. There are alot of new houses being built,some on estates and some in amongst the older town houses.In 1985 some new shops have opened and it is a good place for shopping.Thurs.market. There are about 40 company's in the industrial estate in Nth Walsham. They range from the big company's such as{East Coast Plastics}to some of the smallest company's such as washing machine repairing.The industrial estate was built 13 year's ago in 1972 It was built there because it was the only piece of land available near the bypass away from all the house's. {Drury Haulage & Storage}transport anything from sugarbeet to tined foods,drinks and bricks etc and they have 12 lorries.They travel all over the country and have got 18 employees.
